{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"SlothCreator"}],"role":"article","roleHeading":"Article","title":"Getting Started with Sloths"},"kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Create a sloth and assign personality traits and abilities."}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Essentials","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/tutorials\/SlothCreator","doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth"],"generated":true}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/GettingStarted","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/slothcreator\/gettingstarted"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","type":"heading","anchor":"Overview","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Sloths are complex creatures that require careful creation and a suitable habitat. After creating a sloth, you’re responsible for feeding them, providing fulfilling activities, and giving them opportunities to exercise and rest.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Every sloth has a "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/name","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/color-swift.property"},{"type":"text","text":". You can optionally provide a "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/power-swift.property","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" if your sloth has special supernatural abilities."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"slothPower.png"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"anchor":"Create-a-Sloth","text":"Create a Sloth","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To create a standard sloth without any special supernatural powers, you initialize a new instance of the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" structure, and supply a name and a color, as the following code shows:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["var sloth = Sloth(name: \"Super Sloth\", color: .blue, power: .none)"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If your sloth possesses one of the special powers of ","type":"text"},{"code":"ice","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"fire"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"wind","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"lightning"},{"type":"text","text":", you can specify this at creation:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["var superSloth = Sloth(name: \"Silly Sloth\", color: .green, power: .lightning)"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If you’re creating a large number of sloths, you can define your own random name generator that conforms to the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/NameGenerator"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol, and use it to generate names:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["let slothNamer = MyCustomSlothNamer()","var sloths: [Sloth] = []","","for _ in 0...100 {","    let name = slothNamer.generateName(seed: 0)","    var sloth = Sloth(name: name, color: .green, power: .ice)","    ","    sloths.append(sloth)","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Provide-a-Habitat","level":3,"text":"Provide a Habitat"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Sloths thrive in comfortable habitats. To create a sloth-friendly habitat, you specify whether it’s humid, warm, or both. The following listing creates a habitat that’s humid and warm, which results in a high ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Habitat\/comfortLevel","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["let lovelyHabitat = Habitat(isHumid: true, isWarm: true)"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"After you create a sloth habitat, you’re ready for sloths to sleep in it. Sleeping in a habitat increases the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/energyLevel"},{"text":" of the sloth by the comfort level of the habitat. Sloths sleep for long periods so, by default, your sloth sleeps for 12 hours, but you can also customize this value:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["superSloth.sleep(in: lovelyHabitat)","hyperSloth.sleep(in: lovelyHabitat, for: 2)"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Exercise a Sloth","anchor":"Exercise-a-Sloth"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To keep your sloths happy and fulfilled, you can create activities for them to perform. Define your activities by conforming to the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol and implementing the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity\/perform(with:)","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" method:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["struct Sightseeing: Activity {","    func perform(with sloth: inout Sloth) -> Speed {","        sloth.energyLevel -= 10","        return .slow","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Feed-a-Sloth","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Feed a Sloth"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Sloths require sustenance to perform activities, so you can feed them ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/Food"},{"type":"text","text":". Standard sloth food includes leaves and twigs:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["superSloth.eat(.largeLeaf)","hyperSloth.eat(.twig)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Schedule-Care-for-a-Sloth","text":"Schedule Care for a Sloth","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To make it easy to care for your sloth, SlothCreator provides a ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/CareSchedule","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" structure that lets you define activities or foods for your sloth to enjoy at specific times. Create the schedule, then provide a tuple of a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Date"},{"text":" and an ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":", or you can use some of the standard care procedures:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["let events: [(Date, CareSchedule.Event)] = [","    (Date.now, .bedtime),","    (Date(timeIntervalSinceNow: 12*60*60), .breakfast),","    (Date(timeIntervalSinceNow: 13*60*60), .activity(Sightseeing()))","]","","let schedule = CareSchedule(events: events)","superSloth.schedule = schedule"],"syntax":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://SlothCreator/documentation/SlothCreator/Activity/perform(with:)":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/slothcreator\/activity\/perform(with:)","role":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Performs the work or sequence of actions for an activity."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"perform"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"with","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"inout"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Sloth","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:12SlothCreator0A0V"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Speed","preciseIdentifier":"s:12SlothCreator5SpeedO","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"title":"perform(with:)","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity\/perform(with:)","required":true},"doc://SlothCreator/documentation/SlothCreator/CareSchedule":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/CareSchedule","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"CareSchedule","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"CareSchedule","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"A schedule to maintain the health and happiness of a sloth.","type":"text"}],"title":"CareSchedule","url":"\/documentation\/slothcreator\/careschedule"},"doc://SlothCreator/documentation/SlothCreator/Activity":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Activity"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A type that declares an activity a Sloth can perform."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Activity","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/slothcreator\/activity","title":"Activity","kind":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://SlothCreator/documentation/SlothCreator/Sloth/energyLevel":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/energyLevel","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The energy level of the sloth."}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"energyLevel","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"title":"energyLevel","url":"\/documentation\/slothcreator\/sloth\/energylevel"},"doc://SlothCreator/documentation/SlothCreator/NameGenerator":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/